      "url": "about:srcdoc",
      "title": "EduaakashaA — Gateway to India's Premier Universities",
      "bodyText": "GET COUNSELLING\n● ADMISSIONS 2026 OPEN\nYour Trusted Gateway to India's Premier Universities\n\nExpert guidance for NRI & Indian students navigating DASA, CIWG, TNEA, JOSAA, TANCET — turning ambition into admission.\n\nBook Expert Session →\nExam Schedule 2026\n500+\nSTUDENTS PLACED\n50+\nTOP COLLEGES\n15+\nCOUNTRIES SERVED\nIIT\n♦\nNIT\n♦\nIIIT\n♦\nAnna University\n♦\nVIT\n♦\nSRM\n♦\nBITS Pilani\n♦\nPSG Tech\n♦\nSSN\n♦\nManipal\n♦\nDASA\n♦\nTNEA\n♦\nJOSAA\n♦\nIIT\n♦\nNIT\n♦\nIIIT\n♦\nAnna University\n♦\nVIT\n♦\nSRM\n♦\nBITS Pilani\n♦\nPSG Tech\n♦\nSSN\n♦\nManipal\n♦\nDASA\n♦\nTNEA\n♦\nJOSAA\n♦\nWHAT WE OFFER\nAdmission Services\nEnd-to-end guidance from entrance exams to seat allotment for engineering & management programs.\n🌎\nDASA / CIWG\n\nNRI, PIO & OCI admission to NITs, IIITs and top centrally funded institutes.\n\nNRI EXCLUSIVE\n📐\nTNEA 2026\n\nCutoff analysis, predictions, choice filling and seat matrix for TN Engineering.\n\nTAMIL NADU\n🎯\nJOSAA Guidance\n\nData-driven counselling for IIT, NIT, IIIT and GFTI seat allotment.\n\nALL INDIA\n📚\nTANCET Prep\n\nResources for MBA & MCA admissions in TN government colleges.\n\nPG PROGRAMS\n⚡\nVITEEE for NRI\n\nApplication strategy, campus selection and scholarship guidance for VIT.\n\nPRIVATE UNIV\n💼\nInternships\n\nCurated industry internships to build experience and boost your resume.\n\nCAREER BOOST\nQUICK ACCESS\nExplore All Resources\nEverything you need for your admission journey — all in one place.\n🌎\nDASA / CIWG Guide\nNRI Admissions\n📊\nDASA Seat Matrix\nSeat Availability\n🏫\nIIITs\nNRI Admission\n🏛\nAnna University NRI\nNRI Quota\n🏆\nNIRF Rankings\nCollege Rankings\n📐\nTNEA 2026\nTN Admissions\n📈\nTNEA Matrix\nSeat Data\n💻\nTNEA PC\nPrediction Center\n📉\nTNEA Cutoff\nCutoff Analysis\n🎯\nJOSAA\nIIT/NIT Counselling\n📝\nProfessional Exam\nCompetitive Exams\n💼\nInternship Programs\nIndustry Experience\n🎓\nMBA / MCA Program\nPG Admissions\n📚\nTANCET\nPG Entrance\n💡\nTANCET Pulse\nUpdates & News\n⚡\nVITEEE for NRI\nVIT Entrance\n📖\nEA Library\nResources Hub\n📞\nContact Us\nGet In Touch\nWHO WE SERVE\nTwo Pathways, One Destination\nTailored guidance whether you're an NRI abroad or an Indian student at home.\n🌎\nNRI / PIO / OCI Students\n\nWe simplify DASA, CIWG and NRI quota admissions end-to-end.\n\nDASA & CIWG application support\nNRI quota — Anna University & VIT\nSAT/ACT based admission strategy\nNIRF college shortlisting\nParent counselling sessions\nNRI Admissions →\n🇮🇳\nIndian Domicile Students\n\nStrategic counselling for TNEA, JoSAA, TANCET and professional exams.\n\nTNEA choice filling & cutoff analysis\nJOSAA round-by-round strategy\nTANCET MBA / MCA counselling\nCollege comparison & prediction\nSeat matrix & trend analysis\nIndian Admissions →\nHOW IT WORKS\nFour Steps to Your Dream College\nOur proven framework helps hundreds secure seats at India's top institutions.\n01\n📋\nProfile Assessment\n\nEvaluate scores, eligibility and goals for a personalised roadmap.\n\n02\n🔍\nCollege Shortlisting\n\nNIRF rankings, cutoff trends, seat matrices and placement data.\n\n03\n📝\nApplication Strategy\n\nDocument verification, choice filling and round-by-round planning.\n\n04\n🎉\nSeat Confirmation\n\nFee payment, reporting, hostel and onboarding support.\n\nSTAY CONNECTED\nJoin Our WhatsApp Channels\nGet instant updates, cutoff alerts and expert tips directly on WhatsApp.\nW\nDASA / NRI Updates\nNRI admission alerts & deadlines\nW\nTNEA 2026 Channel\nCutoffs, predictions & counselling\nW\nTANCET\nMBA/MCA exam prep & updates\nW\nJOSAA Counselling\nIIT/NIT allotment strategy\nW\nEduaakashaA Stream Selection\nAll announcements & Stream Selection\nW\nChat with Us\nDirect counsellor support\nReady to Begin Your Journey?\n\nBook a free counselling session. We'll craft the perfect admission strategy for NRI or Indian students.\n\nBook Consultation →\nNRI Admission Guidance\n\nIndia's trusted education consultancy for NRI and domestic students — DASA, TNEA, JOSAA, TANCET and more.\n\nNRI ADMISSIONS\nDASA / CIWG Guide\nDASA Seat Matrix\nIIITs\nAnna University NRI\nVITEEE for NRI\nNIRF Rankings\nINDIAN STUDENTS\nTNEA 2026\nTNEA Matrix\nTNEA Cutoff\nJOSAA\nTANCET\nMBA / MCA\nTANCET Pulse\nRESOURCES\nEA Library\nProfessional Exam\nInternships\nContact Us\nWHATSAPP\nChat with Counsellor\nDASA Channel\nTNEA Channel\n© 2026 EduaakashaA. All rights reserved.\nLinkedIn\nInstagram\nYouTube\nWhatsApp",
